hackrf
------------------------------------------
This repository contains host software (Linux/Windows) for HackRF, a project to
produce a low cost, open source software radio platform.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.3-1
  libfftw3_3-3.3.10-1
  libhackrf-devel-2021.03.1-1bl1
  libhackrf0-2021.03.1-1bl1
  libusb1.0-1.0.21-1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.37-2
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  libusb1.0-devel-1.0.21-1
  ninja-1.10.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://greatscottgadgets.com/hackrf/

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/mossmann/hackrf/archive/refs/tags/v2021.03.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack hackrf-2021.03.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./hackrf-2021.03.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/hackrf-2021.03.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/hackrf-2021.03.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhackrf0-2021.03.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhackrf-devel-2021.03.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(hackrf)
  /usr/bin/hackrf_clock.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_cpldjtag.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_debug.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_info.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_operacake.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_spiflash.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_sweep.exe
  /usr/bin/hackrf_transfer.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/hackrf.README
  /usr/share/doc/hackrf/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/hackrf/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/hackrf/TRADEMARK

(libhackrf0)
  /usr/bin/cyghackrf-0.dll

(libhackrf-devel)
  /usr/include/libhackrf/hackrf.h
  /usr/lib/libhackrf.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libhackrf.pc

